{"tid":1733522,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[置頂] 參考1945年布達佩斯圍城戰，死守傷亡遠低於突圍。","createTime":"2019-11-18T06:20:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T06:34:04.000Z","uid":300697,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5222e6142bcd524ea63b3701b962367c2dc15da5","tid":1733522,"uid":300697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T06:20:39.000Z","msg":"1945年2月11日晚上有<span style=\"color: red;\">25,000</span>名德軍及匈牙利軍開始從城堡山走下來，他們分成3批，每一批裡有數千名平民，整個家庭推著嬰兒車，蹅著冰雪出來，<span style=\"color: red;\">不幸地，蘇軍正等待這些逃亡者。</span><br />\n<br />\n軍隊及平民利用霧作掩護，第一批出來時令蘇軍士兵及炮兵目瞪口呆，因此有一些人逃脫，但第2批及第3批就沒有這麼幸運，蘇軍大炮及火箭彈飛向逃走區，造成多人死亡，雖然付出慘重代價，但<span style=\"color: green;\">5,000至10,000人</span>安全逃至布達佩斯西北面的山林地帶及向維也納走去，大約7,000名德軍逃脫了。<span style=\"color: red;\">大部份試圖逃脫的人被殺、受傷或被蘇軍俘虜，德匈聯軍指揮官維登布魯赫及欣迪亦被俘虜。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">傷亡率超過一半<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>，<span style=\"color: green;\">守住先，我們想下方法救人。俾一日時間我們！</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%B8%83%E9%81%94%E4%BD%A9%E6%96%AF%E5%9C%8D%E5%9F%8E%E6%88%B0#%E5%BE%B7%E8%BB%8D%E7%AC%AC3%E6%AC%A1%E9%80%B2%E6%94%BB%EF%BC%88%E6%88%96%E7%AA%81%E5%9C%8D%EF%BC%89%E5%8F%8A%E6%8A%95%E9%99%8D\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E5%25B8%2583%25E9%2581%2594%25E4%25BD%25A9%25E6%2596%25AF%25E5%259C%258D%25E5%259F%258E%25E6%2588%25B0%23%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E8%25BB%258D%25E7%25AC%25AC3%25E6%25AC%25A1%25E9%2580%25B2%25E6%2594%25BB%25EF%25BC%2588%25E6%2588%2596%25E7%25AA%2581%25E5%259C%258D%25EF%25BC%2589%25E5%258F%258A%25E6%258A%2595%25E9%2599%258D&d=uhXF1s3LJRzyxl6IDZpy2SwbHaueoKb2XZOoGTcnCr8%3D&h=1387fe73\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%B8%83%E9%81%94%E4%BD%A9%E6%96%AF%E5%9C%8D%E5%9F%8E%E6%88%B0#%E5%BE%B7%E8%BB%8D%E7%AC%AC3%E6%AC%A1%E9%80%B2%E6%94%BB%EF%BC%88%E6%88%96%E7%AA%81%E5%9C%8D%EF%BC%89%E5%8F%8A%E6%8A%95%E9%99%8D</a>"},{"pid":"2f3d590f5636c64b6b008a00242d7d55accd1399","tid":1733522,"uid":88019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T06:21:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab9575a51383f5d34f6d22adea00fe2b12f13844","tid":1733522,"uid":150466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T06:22:59.000Z","msg":"夠資源留守就留，唔夠就棄裝投降啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4469a24952b85635f8ee69d4210c5430b401f15a","tid":1733522,"uid":332362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T06:30:56.000Z","msg":"中美最高層正在電話商談落實第ㄧ階段貿易協議 政府不敢再升級的。<br />\n加上警狗絶對不敢攻入大學 國際是極不容許的 暫宜短暫休息吧。"},{"pid":"18ac9e285658894294fda0ef72beee1ebc084d88","tid":1733522,"uid":233228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T06:32:33.000Z","msg":"攞徐蚌會戰比可能更值得參考<br />\n吸引精銳<br />\n最後包圍全殲<br />\n因為冇資源同冇地形優勢"},{"pid":"229f737ffb2678994d785b0dc73636cadf3959a0","tid":1733522,"uid":300697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"18ac9e285658894294fda0ef72beee1ebc084d88","tid":1733522,"uid":233228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T06:32:33.000Z","msg":"攞徐蚌會戰比可能更值得參考<br />\n吸引精銳<br />\n最後包圍全殲<br />\n因為冇資源同冇地形優勢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T06:34:04.000Z","msg":"我只讀過世史唔係咁知道。"}]}